main event: A report of a UFO sighting over Waikiki Beach, Hawaii, on June 29, 1966.
interesting points: The object was described as oval-shaped, 50 to 60 feet long, emitting a white light and five blinking lights in between., The object left a vapor trail with sparks and had flames that emerged one at a time., The sighting lasted for approximately 2 minutes., A highly educated female witness, aged 53, observed the event during a night tour., The report mentioned considerable public concern regarding a possible meteor/satellite burn out incident.
witness description: a highly educated lady, aged 53, freelance artist
